bubbles.pl - Draw SMART domain bubbles

Uses gimp and Gimp::Fu to automatically draw domain bubbles.

Requires:
-Gimp (http://www.gimp.org) : if you use Linux, you probably have Gimp already 
installed 
-Gimp::Fu (Gimp perl module) : avaliable at your neares CPAN mirror

Using:

-just copy bubbles.pl to your ~/.gimp-1.2/plug-ins/ and you'll have a new entry
in Gimp under Xtns->Perl-Fu menu called SMART Bubbles

-to use it in batch mode, see run_batch.pl for an example 
